These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, tiparillo, siglo
House: victorian, townhouse, farmhouse
3 different games are played: chess, bridge, scrabble
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, superhero, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, funk
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, mauve, grey
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, begonia
 1. the fan of ambient is the townhouse house##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 4. the person playing chess is the person who likes grey##1
 5. the person who growslily is between the farmhouse house and the siglo-smoker##2
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is in an odd position##4
 7. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
 9. the townhouse house is between the person who likes green and the fan of country##2
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person playing bridge##1
11. the person who growslily is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who likes grey##2
12. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
13. the person who growsbegonia is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |         3          |
| Cigar      | siglo | game     | tiparillo      |
| House          | victorian | townhouse | farmhouse               |
| Game           | chess   | bridge   | scrabble |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | superhero | thriller           |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   | funk               |
| Color   | grey  | mauve   | green           |
| Flower           | zinnia   | lily      | begonia              |

