.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, lemonade
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, oliveros, old-henry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, musical, satire
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, rock, salsa
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, cottage
