 5. the oliveros-smoker is the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is between the cottage house and the gothic-revival house##2
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 9. the fan of salsa is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking tea##2
11. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage          | tea      | lemonade        | iced-tea        |
| Cigar           | oliveros | old-henry | dunhill    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire       | musical        | fantasy       |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | rock           | salsa         |
| House   | gothic-revival    | art-deco         | cottage          |
| Transport           | bus         | subway           | taxi    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | magic-tricks     | collecting |

